rodando compose 
docker-compose up --build -d

# Sobe apenas o banco e mensageria
docker-compose up postgres rabbitmq -d



Adicionar no docker-compose quando for subir a app:

services:
  api:
    build:
      context: .
      dockerfile: ./src/Delivery.WebApi/Dockerfile
    container_name: rentalsystem_api
    ports:
      - "5000:80"
    depends_on:
      - postgres
      - rabbitmq


migrations
na pasta src
dotnet ef migrations add ChangeTablesName --project RentalSystem.Infra --startup-project RentalSystem.Presentation

dotnet ef database update --project RentalSystem.Infra --startup-project RentalSystem.Presentation

dotnet ef database drop --project RentalSystem.Infra --startup-project RentalSystem.Presentation
rollback

dotnet ef database update NomeDaMigration


acessando banco de dados no Docker

docker exec -it rentalsystem_postgres psql -U admin -d rentalsystemdb

docker-compose up -d rabbitmq
